 102:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     [..]
 103:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (@) These interfaces allow to manage a sequential transfer with a repeated start condition
 104:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****           when a direction change during transfer
 105:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****     [..]
 106:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) A specific option field manage the different steps of a sequential transfer
 107:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) Option field values are defined through I2C_XFEROPTIONS and are listed below:
 108:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_AND_LAST_FRAME: No sequential usage, functional is same as associated interfac
 109:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****            no sequential mode
 110:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequence with start con
 111:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and data to transfer without a final stop condition
 112:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_FIRST_AND_NEXT_FRAME: Sequential usage (Master only), this option allow to manage a 
 113:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             start condition, address and data to transfer without a final stop cond
 114:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             an then permit a call the same master sequential interface several time
 115:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             (like HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_IT() then HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit
 116:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             or HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_DMA() then HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_D
 117:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_NEXT_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequence with a restart 
 118:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and with new data to transfer if the direction change or manage only th
 119:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             transfer
 120:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             if no direction change and without a final stop condition in both cases
 121:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_LAST_FRAME: Sequential usage, this option allow to manage a sequance with a restart 
 122:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             and with new data to transfer if the direction change or manage only th
 123:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             transfer
 124:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             if no direction change and with a final stop condition in both cases
 125:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****       (++) I2C_LAST_FRAME_NO_STOP: Sequential usage (Master only), this option allow to manage a re
 126:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             after several call of the same master sequential interface several time
 127:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             (link with option I2C_FIRST_AND_NEXT_FRAME).
 128:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                             Usage can, transfer several bytes one by one using
 129:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_IT
 130:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               or HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Receive_IT
 131:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               or HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Transmit_DMA
 132:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               or HAL_I2C_Master_Seq_Receive_DMA
 133:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               with option I2C_FIRST_AND_NEXT_FRAME then I2C_NEXT_FRAME.
 134:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                              Then usage of this option I2C_LAST_FRAME_NO_STOP at the last Transmit 
 135:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_i2c.c ****                               Receive sequence permit to call the opposite interface Receive or Tra
